Description: Aptura Classic XFCE desktop integration
 Installs Aptura's XFCE integration, desktop launchers, and utility hooks.
 The default desktop uses XFCE and LightDM with Aptura Classic window borders,
 a Windows 3.1/95 inspired color system, practical workstation tools, firmware
 visibility, power controls, and a local system health check.
